===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*teh₂g-|id=order}}
Comes from the Greek word 'taxis' which comes from Ottoman Turkish تقسیم‎, from Arabic تَقْسِيم‎ (taqsīm), verbal noun of قَسَمَ‎ (qasama, “to divide into parts / clsesses”).  

